---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="YWAM Sendai | Modern Monastic-Missional Community" lang="en" isSnap={true}>
  <main>
    
    <section class="h-screen w-full snap-start relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <img src="/hero-sendai.jpg" alt="Sendai Landscape" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40 grayscale-[0.2]" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/10 via-transparent to-dark-bg"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative z-10">
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-9xl font-serif tracking-tighter mb-4">Sendai.</h1>
        <p class="text-gold-accent tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-xs md:text-sm font-light italic">A Modern Monastic-Missional Community</p>
      </div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-10 animate-bounce opacity-30 text-[10px] tracking-[0.5em]">SCROLL</div>
    </section>

    <section class="min-h-screen w-full snap-start bg-dark-bg p-8 flex flex-col justify-center">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <span class="text-gold-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-widest block mb-6 text-center">Our Primary Calling</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-center mb-12 italic">Deeply Hidden in Christ.</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="space-y-6 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            <p>
              We believe that the most effective way to reach Japan is through a life <span class="text-zinc-100">transformed</span>. Our transformation becomes the light that draws others to Him.
            </p>
            <p>
              Since 2018, YWAM Sendai has served as a <span class="italic text-gold-accent">Mission Hub</span> for the Tohoku region—a spiritual engine room fueling the expansion of the Kingdom across North Japan.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 p-8 rounded-[2.5rem]">
            <h3 class="text-zinc-100 font-bold mb-4 uppercase text-xs tracking-widest">The Heart of the Mission Hub</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm">
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-gold-accent">†</span> Intimacy as Mission (Theosis)</li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-gold-accent">†</span> Deep Contextualization</li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-gold-accent">†</span> Faithful Longevity</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="min-h-screen w-full snap-start bg-zinc-950 p-6 flex flex-col justify-center">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full">
        <span class="text-gold-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-widest block mb-6 text-center">University of the Nations</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif mb-12 text-center italic text-white">Formation of the Missionary</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          
          <div class="group relative overflow-hidden bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-10 rounded-[3rem] hover:border-gold-accent/50 transition-all flex flex-col">
            <h3 class="text-gold-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">The Foundation</h3>
            <h4 class="text-4xl font-serif mb-4 italic text-white">DTS</h4>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-8 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
              A foundational "Live-Learn" experience. More than a course, it is an invitation to be transformed by the character of God and join His mission through a 5-month lecture and field assignment.
            </p>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-t border-zinc-800 pt-6">
              <div class="flex flex-col">
                <span class="text-[10px] text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Next School</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-zinc-300 font-bold">24 Sept 2026</span>
              </div>
              <a href="/en/dts" class="text-xs font-bold underline underline-offset-8 hover:text-gold-accent transition-colors">LEARN MORE</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group relative overflow-hidden bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-10 rounded-[3rem] hover:border-gold-accent/50 transition-all flex flex-col">
            <h3 class="text-gold-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Bible Immersion</h3>
            <h4 class="text-4xl font-serif mb-4 italic text-white">DBS</h4>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-8 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
              12 weeks. 66 books. One unified story. Discover God's redemptive work through an inductive study of the Word, from Genesis to Revelation. 
              <span class="block mt-2 text-[10px] italic opacity-60">*Prerequisite: DTS</span>
            </p>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-t border-zinc-800 pt-6">
              <div class="flex flex-col">
                <span class="text-[10px] text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Next School</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-zinc-300 font-bold">Apr 2027</span>
              </div>
              <a href="/en/dbs" class="text-xs font-bold underline underline-offset-8 hover:text-gold-accent transition-colors">LEARN MORE</a>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="min-h-screen w-full snap-start bg-dark-bg p-8 flex flex-col justify-center">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif mb-16 italic text-zinc-400">The Tohoku Mandate</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 text-left">
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="h-px w-12 bg-gold-accent mb-6"></div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">The Mission Hub</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">Sendai provides the resources, training, and spiritual oversight necessary to pioneer new teams across every prefecture.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="h-px w-12 bg-gold-accent mb-6"></div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">Slow Mission</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">We value the aesthetic of beauty and presenting Christianity as an ancient "Way" that belongs in the Japanese story.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="h-px w-12 bg-gold-accent mb-6"></div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">The Movement</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">We labour to see a vibrant YWAM presence established in every one of the six prefectures of North Japan.</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="h-screen w-full snap-start flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif mb-6 text-white italic">An Invitation to the Way.</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-500 mb-12 max-w-sm text-sm font-sans">
        We invite the pioneers, the contemplatives, the artists, and the scholars. Join us as we labour for the hearts of Tohoku.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 w-full max-w-xs font-sans">
        <button class="open-hub-trigger w-full py-5 bg-gold-accent text-black font-black rounded-full hover:scale-105 transition-transform uppercase tracking-widest text-xs cursor-pointer">
          Connect
        </button>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>